    <span>Down:</span>

    <br>
    1. to be preoccupied with a single topic or emotion - <b>obsessed</b>
    <br>
    3. to move slowly and quietly in a particular direction - <b>creep</b>
    <br>
    4. orderly, logical and Consistent - <b>coherent</b>
    <br>

    <br>
    <span>Across</span>:
    <br>
    2. to utter rapidly or unintelligibly - <b>babble</b>
    <br>
    5. to insert something between other things - <b>interpose</b>
    <br>
    6. an unreadable handwriting - <b>squiggle</b>
